    <p>We are excited to announce our highly anticipated event of the year is back! Join us in INSTELLAR 2024, proudly presented by <strong>Theme and Strategic Studies, Political Science, and Advocacy of PPIA</strong>, a prestigious event that celebrates the achievements and contributions of international students.</p>

    <p class="highlight">What is INSTELLAR?</p>
    <p>INSTELLAR stands for <strong>Inspirational Talents, Scholars, and Intellectual Symposium for Outstanding Leaders of All Regions</strong>. The event is designed to provide a platform for students to showcase their talents, engage in intellectual discussions, and connect with peers from different backgrounds.</p>

    <p class="highlight">Event Highlights:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Panels:</strong> Discussions on current global issues and the inspiring narratives of both prominent and emerging leaders</li>
      <li><strong>Workshops:</strong> Interactive sessions to develop skills and knowledge</li>
      <li><strong>Talent Show:</strong> Showcase your unique talents and compete for exciting prizes</li>
      <li><strong>Networking Sessions:</strong> Build connections with peers, alumni, and industry professionals</li>
    </ul>

    <p>INSTELLAR 2024 promises to be bigger and better, bringing you more insightful discussions, fun-filled workshops, and the opportunity to showcase your talents on a grand stage.</p>

    <p class="highlight">Join Our Committee!</p>
    <p>We are looking for passionate and dedicated individuals to be part of the organizing team. Gain invaluable experience in event management and be part of this memorable event.</p>

    <p class="highlight">Recruitment Details:</p>
    <p><strong>Batch 1 Registration:</strong> May 21, 2024</p>
    <p><strong>Available Divisions:</strong></p>
